metadata.name: ATEC HQ
metadata.description:
The AVANTECTURE HQ serves as the strategic control center for our studio in the metaverse, a museum of inspirational art and a clubhouse for owners of our NFTs

All AVANTECTURE NFTs are metaverse ready, built in 3D and rendered in 4k. Upon purchase, the NFT owner will get access to the 3D files and 2D plans. Technical support for a later integration on Metaverse is provided.
